That report seemed to open the floodgates. Next, The Shade Room published more photos and videos of Thompson entering his hotel with a woman and showed her later leaving a large bag.

Finally, TMZ unearthed security shots taken in a hookah room in Washington DC last October. It showed that Thompson was approaching two women.

Neither the 33-year-old reality star, who called his 20-month romance with Thompson his "best" union, nor the NBA champion have commented on the reports, but privately, a source tells E ! News: "She feels defeated." Fortunately, she has her best cheerleaders by her side. Mama Kris Jenner of 62 years, and sisters Kourtney of 38 years, and Kim of 37 years, have joined her, says another source: "They wanted that was comfortable and not stressed at all. "
